Class PSAttributeList

All Implemented Interfaces:
IPSComponent, IPSDatabaseComponent, Cloneable
public class PSAttributeList
extends PSDatabaseComponentCollection
implements IPSComponent

This class defines a set of attributes stored as a database component. Each attribute will be defined as a mapping from a name (type String) and a collection of values (The collection will contain String objects.

toXml

public Element toXml(Document doc)
This method is called to create a PSXAttributeList XML element node containing the data described in this object.

The structure of the XML document is: 


 <!ELEMENT PSXAttributeList (PSXAttribute*)>
 <!ATTLIST PSXAttributeList
    id CDATA #REQUIRED
 >
